snippet.title: Wave 5 of the Mario Kart 8 Deluxe – Booster Course Pass launches July 12th!
snippet.description:
Available to buy now: https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Nintendo-Switch-games/Mario-Kart-8-Deluxe-1173281.html?utm_medium=social&utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=MarioKart8Deluxe%7CBCP5AN%7Cm_id_aUQrAMZwWm%7C1173281#Booster_Course_Pass

Pump up those tyres, Wave 5 is almost here! Eight additional courses and three returning characters come to the Mario Kart 8 Deluxe – Booster Course Pass on July 12th.
